# reroll-dashboards — environment variables
# Copy to .env for local development.
# On Streamlit Cloud, set these as secrets in the project settings (not as env vars).
#
# These credentials use the viz_reader role — SELECT on gold/silver/bronze schemas only.
# Never use ingest_user or dbt_analytics here.

